tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE weather_data (
  date DATE,
  temperature FLOAT,
  humidity FLOAT,
  wind_speed FLOAT,
  energy_consumption FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE historical_weather_data (
  weather_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  city_name VARCHAR(50),
  date DATE,
  temperature INT,
  humidity INT
);

CREATE TABLE energy_consumption (
  consumption_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  city_name VARCHAR(50),
  consumption_date DATE,
  energy_type VARCHAR(50),
  consumption_amount INT
);

CREATE TABLE energy_consumption (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    energy_usage FLOAT,
    building_id INT,
    power_consumption FLOAT,
    voltage FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE heating_cooling_systems (
    system_id INT,
    system_type VARCHAR(255),
    installation_date DATE,
    efficiency FLOAT,
    status VARCHAR(50)
);
